632
00:40:30,539 --> 00:40:32,599
[SPEAKER_01] Pa tako i kad nešto nam promakne,

633
00:40:32,599 --> 00:40:33,820
[SPEAKER_01] kad nešto zeznemo,

634
00:40:33,820 --> 00:40:36,219
[SPEAKER_01] kad ih krivo optužimo za neke stvari,

635
00:40:36,219 --> 00:40:37,199
