636
00:40:37,199 --> 00:40:38,360
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo nagli.

637
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:39,820
[SPEAKER_01] Svega tu bude,

638
00:40:39,820 --> 00:40:40,920
[SPEAKER_01] naravno, to je jedna živa.

639
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:42,059
[SPEAKER_01] To je živi organizam,

640
