641
00:40:43,239 --> 00:40:45,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što je zlatno pravilo

642
00:40:45,599 --> 00:40:46,440
[SPEAKER_01] u našoj obitelji

643
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:47,599
[SPEAKER_01] je da smo autentični

644
00:40:47,599 --> 00:40:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] i da se znamo jednim drugima ispričati.

645
00:40:49,539 --> 00:40:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da funkcionira.

646
00:40:51,940 --> 00:40:52,820
[SPEAKER_01] Mi se jako volimo

647
00:40:52,820 --> 00:40:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] i funkcioniramo

648
00:40:53,679 --> 00:40:55,059
