654
00:41:04,199 --> 00:41:06,440
[SPEAKER_03] Skroz mi je izlizala se skroz.

655
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:08,900
[SPEAKER_03] A jedna recimo prekrasna riječ

656
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:09,780
[SPEAKER_03] koju si mi rekla,

657
00:41:09,780 --> 00:41:12,800
[SPEAKER_03] rekla si stvarni.

658
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:14,119
[SPEAKER_03] Da se trudite

659
