664
00:41:22,260 --> 00:41:23,780
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je to jedno te isto.

665
00:41:23,780 --> 00:41:26,159
[SPEAKER_01] Autentično jest stvarno.

666
00:41:26,159 --> 00:41:26,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što je

667
