730
00:43:09,699 --> 00:43:11,179
[SPEAKER_01] Tako ćemo mijenjati

731
00:43:11,179 --> 00:43:12,760
[SPEAKER_01] jako puno tih navika.

732
00:43:12,760 --> 00:43:13,900
[SPEAKER_01] Primjeri se u komunikaciji.

733
00:43:13,900 --> 00:43:16,159
[SPEAKER_03] Kako to napraviti?

734
00:43:16,159 --> 00:43:17,860
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, evo, ako želiš

735
00:43:17,860 --> 00:43:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] bih zaista stvaran,

736
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:19,820
