744
00:43:29,900 --> 00:43:31,679
[SPEAKER_01] To je meni u mom životu

745
00:43:31,679 --> 00:43:32,360
[SPEAKER_01] jako važno.

746
00:43:32,360 --> 00:43:33,679
[SPEAKER_01] To su moje vrijednosti.

747
00:43:33,679 --> 00:43:35,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam pokušala,

748
