766
00:44:06,219 --> 00:44:07,119
[SPEAKER_01] Trolovi.

767
00:44:07,119 --> 00:44:08,480
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu to, nisu trolovi,

768
00:44:08,480 --> 00:44:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] to nisu hejteri.

769
00:44:09,519 --> 00:44:11,519
[SPEAKER_01] To su ljudi koji se ne znaju ljepše

770
