783
00:44:30,599 --> 00:44:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] Za ovo drugo bi trebali imati truda,

784
00:44:32,880 --> 00:44:34,739
[SPEAKER_01] stat, razmisliti,

785
00:44:34,739 --> 00:44:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] ljepše se izraziti,

786
00:44:35,960 --> 00:44:37,159
[SPEAKER_01] oslaniti se na dojama,

787
