[SPEAKER_01] ne na zaključak odmah.

788
00:44:38,400 --> 00:44:39,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ne skakati pred rudo,

789
00:44:39,739 --> 00:44:41,239
[SPEAKER_01] ne skakati jedni drugima za vrat.

790
00:44:41,239 --> 00:44:43,079
[SPEAKER_01] Zato treba vremena i truda.

791
00:44:43,079 --> 00:44:44,219
[SPEAKER_01] To nije jednostavno.

792
00:44:44,219 --> 00:44:46,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ali prihvaćanje je upravo to,

793
00:44:46,380 --> 00:44:47,619
