796
00:44:53,659 --> 00:44:55,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ili kužiš, znači,

797
00:44:55,360 --> 00:44:56,780
[SPEAKER_01] to je autentično.

798
00:44:56,780 --> 00:44:58,139
[SPEAKER_01] A ne da ja kažem,

799
