806
00:45:13,079 --> 00:45:14,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ali opet da ne pretjerujem.

807
00:45:14,500 --> 00:45:17,619
[SPEAKER_01] Da ne idem okolo i sad sve prolazi.

808
00:45:17,619 --> 00:45:18,679
[SPEAKER_01] Nemam granica.

809
00:45:18,860 --> 00:45:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] To bi bilo drugi dio to kontinuum.

810
00:45:23,559 --> 00:45:25,800
[SPEAKER_01] To je kad si pretjero vlastitim vrijednostima,

811
00:45:25,800 --> 00:45:27,739
[SPEAKER_01] kad si pretjero u autentičnosti.

812
00:45:27,739 --> 00:45:29,460
[SPEAKER_01] To se isto može dogoditi.

813
00:45:29,460 --> 00:45:30,980
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kad si sam sebi,

814
00:45:30,980 --> 00:45:31,920
