817
00:45:35,019 --> 00:45:36,860
[SPEAKER_01] da onda kolješ sve oko sebe s tim.

818
00:45:36,860 --> 00:45:39,460
[SPEAKER_01] E to negdje između...

819
00:45:39,460 --> 00:45:41,960
[SPEAKER_03] Često danas pominješ te riječi koljem.

820
00:45:42,079 --> 00:45:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] Da, o tom je danas riječ dana

821
00:45:44,079 --> 00:45:44,860
[SPEAKER_01] i spričavam se.

822
00:45:44,860 --> 00:45:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] Jesam, ali ovo mi je jako srastveno tema.

823
00:45:46,579 --> 00:45:47,139
[SPEAKER_03] Je, super.

824
00:45:47,139 --> 00:45:48,300
[SPEAKER_03] Hvala, samo rastaj, molim.

825
00:45:48,300 --> 00:45:49,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, dobro je znati...

826
00:45:49,500 --> 00:45:50,760
[SPEAKER_03] Svoj što sam te prekinio.

827
00:45:50,760 --> 00:45:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] Uništio sam i flow.

828
00:45:52,800 --> 00:45:53,579
[SPEAKER_01] Jesam, da.

829
00:45:53,579 --> 00:45:55,380
